data.description: Modern Townhome on a Peaceful Street Welcome to 1112 S 12th Ave E, Newton, IA 50208. This stylish townhome has been thoughtfully updated, featuring a new roof, facia, shutters, and down spouts in 2023, fresh interior paint, and new carpet throughout. The kitchen boasts all-new stainless steel/black appliances, while the main floor offers laundry hookups for convenience. With 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, including a master with a 3/4 en suite, there's room for everyone. The basement has a bonus family room and ample storage. At approximately 2,000 total livable square feet (including the partially finished basement), this townhome offers a comfortable and spacious living environment. Plus, the HOA takes care of snow removal for the private road, making your life easier. Don't miss this opportunity to call this tranquil townhome your own. Contact us today to see it for yourself!
